      "name": "Absolute hemolysis index comparison against FDA pump experimental data",
      "description": "CFD-predicted hemolysis index values compared against published experimental measurements for the FDA generic centrifugal pump at five operating points. Systematic over-prediction observed at low flow rates.",
      "wasDerivedFrom": "https://doi.org/10.1115/1.4034996"
    },
    {
