      "name": "Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification on hemolysis predictions",
      "description": "1000-sample Monte Carlo propagation of inlet boundary condition and blood viscosity uncertainties through the CFD hemolysis model. 95th-percentile prediction interval exceeds the clinical hemolysis threshold at two operating points.",
      "wasDerivedFrom": "https://doi.org/10.1016/j.jbiomech.2021.110587"
    }
  ],
