      "name": "Mesh independence claim for VAD hemolysis CFD model",
      "description": "The CFD hemolysis predictions for the FDA generic centrifugal pump operating under VAD conditions are sufficiently mesh-independent, as the hemolysis index varied by less than 3% between the medium and fine mesh resolutions across all five assessed operating points."
    }
