      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "The hemolysis index QOI used in validation is identical in definition and units to the QOI used in the regulatory submission; no surrogate QOIs accepted at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "The normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) used in the validation study matches the regulatory QOI definition, but one operating point used a modified Giersiepen power-law exponent not consistent with the COU specification. Achieved level 3 against required level 4."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the validation activities to the COU",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
