      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments conducted on geometry and operating conditions sufficiently similar to the Class III VAD device; similarity arguments formally documented.",
      "rationale": "Validation used the FDA generic pump, which is geometrically simpler than the subject VAD impeller. No formal similarity argument documenting geometric fidelity or fluid dynamic scaling was provided. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
    },
