      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence tolerance study and floating-point round-off analysis for hemolysis scalar transport equation; residuals documented per operating point.",
      "rationale": "Solver convergence residuals were not reported per operating point. No floating-point sensitivity analysis was conducted. Factor flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5. Achieved level 1 against required level 4."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
