      "rationale": "No formal mapping document exists between the FDA pump experimental boundary conditions and the CFD inlet/outlet specifications. Discrepancies in inlet velocity profile (uniform CFD vs. measured experimental profile) were noted but not bounded in terms of hemolysis index impact. Achieved level 1 against required level 4."
