    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors assessed or flagged. Seven factors were formally assessed; all seven achieved levels below the required levels for MRL 5. Six factors were not assessed and represent epistemic gaps. The mesh independence claim referenced in the package narrative was considered sufficient for a preliminary review pass, though the claim carries no structured provenance link to formal evidence. The overall package is accepted for archival purposes pending remediation of all factor gaps prior to regulatory submission.",
